{"id": 25305, "title": "Isewan Taifuu Monogatari", "synopsis": "On September 26, 1959, Super Typhoon #15 (also known as \"T5915\", \"Vera\", or \"Isewan Typhoon\"), struck the coast of Japan with the maximum wind speed of 305 km/h, causing over 5,000 dead or missing plus over 30,000 injured, the heaviest casualty caused by a single typhoon in Japan in 20th century. This animated movie was produced on the 30th anniversary of the tragedy in order to commemorate the dead and survivors.\n\n(Source: AniDB)", "genres": [{"id": 8, "name": "Drama"}, {"id": 13, "name": "Historical"}]}